ServerDefaultPage - ChangeLog
=============================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Method installConfFile() from httpd server packages has been removed in i-MSCP 1.3.0
    Fixed: onAddIps() was not able to use $self
    Enhancement: Only trigger listener if status is enabled
    Enhancement: Enhancement: Avoid usage of experimental smartmatch operator

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Only add BASE_SERVER_IP to ssl ips, if ssl is enabled for panel
    Fixed: Compatibility with i-MSCP 1.2.17 API

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Certificate path in vhost-file

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Always support SSL

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: iMSCP::Dir::make expects the mode passed as octal value
    CS fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: README.md file (Added note about template customization)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.1.x serie
    Updated: Templates

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Possibility to define an own certificate

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: CS issues

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Smartmatch is experimental ...

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Forbidden access to css and image files ( Apache >= 2.4 )
    Removed: Useless configuration file

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Useless instantiation of Httpd server

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Release: First released version
